title: Our Thoughts on Casey Neistat's Return to Vlogging
description:
Podcast Channel: https://youtu.be/sQ6o4XWZfZY
This week we talk about Casey Neistat's return to vlogging and the impact Casey has had on the YouTube platform as well as our careers. We talk about where the platform was when he first started vlogging and where the platform is today and ask the question - is there room today for another daily vlogger?
itunes:author: Colin and Samir
